name: imperfect drawings #1
description:
Animated GIF | 6 fps| 2048 x 2048 | RGB | sRGB IEC61966-2.1 

With this animated GIF, I tried to recreate the same motif of a back over and over again, without the use of onion layers. With this approach, I show the generally imprecise line work of the human hand. Even though the technical capabilities of digital software can bring digital art to perfection, I prefer to illustrate the imperfection. Simply because this is where I see the beauty. 

DG
